								<p>
									<div class="row">
										<div class="col md8 s8">
										<input type="checkbox" id="shelter" />
										<label for="shelter">Animal that is lost, running-at large, or stray.</label>
										</div>
										<div class="col md4 s4">
										<span class="badge orange" id="learn-more-shelter">Learn more &#9654;</span>
										</div>

									</div>

								</p>
								<div id="shelter-more-info" class="hidden">
									Any shelter must be proportional to the animal size, have at least three walls, a waterproof roof, and protects the animal for regional from the elements.
									<br><br>
									<a href="#">Learn more about this law</a>
								</div>

								<p>
								<div class="row">
										<div class="col md8 s8">
											<input type="checkbox" id="conditions" />
