										</div>
										<div class="col md4 s4 right" >
											<span class="badge orange" id="learn-more-conditions">Learn more &#9654;</span>
										</div>
								</div>
								</p>
								<div id="conditions-more-info" class="hidden">
									Sanitation: Animals must be in a space free of excretions and other waste materials, dirt and trash that may be a health hazard.
									<br>
									Food & Water: Animals need access to portable drinking water and edible food.
									<br><br>
									<a href="#">Learn more about this law</a>
								</div>

								<p>
								<div class="row">
										<div class="col md8 s8">
											<input type="checkbox" id="outside" />
											<label for="outside">Animal attacks, bites, or otherwise dangerous animals</label>
										</div>
										<div class="col md4 s4">
										<span class="badge orange" id="learn-more-outside">Learn more &#9654;</span>
										</div>
								</div>
								</p>
								<div id="outside-more-info" class="hidden">
									Animals may be left outside if the following conditions are met: 
									<ul>
										<li>- Animal is not outside for more than half an hour when the temperature is below 32 F or above 90 F.</li>
										<li>- The animal has access to portable drinking water, edible food, and adequate shade or shelter.</li>
									</ul>
									<a href="#">Learn more about this law</a>
								</div>

								<p>
								<div class="row">
